messages.message:
hey team, noticing some build issues on aihub-sandbox
• when u create a new field, extraction doesn't immediately start and there's no run button --> you have to exit the field and extraction will start (ss1)
• for any new fields added, the prompt is being sent twice which is causing extraction errors (ss2)

hmm could this be related to your changes to the `uuid` for new fields? @jaden

can you take a look today? we should try to fix before 25.34 code cut on monday

i was able to reproduce on aihub-sandbox

notice how the new field (in my case, `employer name` ) was included twice in the request body to `/extraction`

Have a PR ready with the correct fix now https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/73680 !

edit: merged!
